  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effect of escalation of radiation dose to tumor and lymph nodes based on
      an inhomogeneous dose distribution controlled by FDG-PET positive areas compared to a
      standard homogeneous dose spread
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
